cs.RO, cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a method for social robots to interact with passersby without causing discomfort. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also likely as the paper discusses the importance of adapting robot behavior to the situation and the results of an experiment in the field. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the proposed method uses reinforcement learning to enable robots to greet passersby in a user-centered manner. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is possible as the paper may involve visual recognition of passersby to determine appropriate behavior. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the proposed method involves reinforcement learning.
